.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"陣間試下先 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac004a588bdc3ac98787e66294bcc99e0bbfa5ca","tid":764561,"uid":61755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770d8d147389befad14287c7a041b012ff63e782","tid":764561,"uid":89567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3768d30d52456fd450ea99b24da0692ddc1089b8","tid":764561,"uid":72952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"係咪用膠水兜/食物兜?<br />\n如果係就要換"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔係呀 用緊陶瓷碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:18:56.000Z","msg":"可能括花左個表面 易積菌<br />\n換左隻碗佢啦<br />\n之前有黑下巴 睇過獸醫 <br />\n叫我地換左個水機 唔洗食藥搽藥 幾個月自然好番哂"},{"pid":"b2b2345a70844f5848990d56f2cadb743e34a5c3","tid":764561,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"通常貓公會咁<br />\n荷爾蒙過多<br />\n<br />\n仲有個原因係糧兜唔乾淨"},{"pid":"1795f1ec70aac37c91b28d8d18ffd95b5f684009","tid":764561,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"好似話用不鏽鋼糧兜會好D"},{"pid":"1800e506c291e9306145603db45ad97d78938da9","tid":764561,"uid":193408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:54:41.000Z","msg":"多數可能係啲糧太油"},{"pid":"fccb8e81ed726cb8fc6bef41e823fcc2fa841bd2","tid":764561,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"之前養3隻得一隻有生<br />\n有得閒幫佢摔下下巴仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知摔到愈來愈少毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又紅紅地<br />\n跟住唔鬼理佢<br />\n過一排就無左<br />\n中間有轉過糧唔知開唔開事"},{"pid":"3b786aa8e1f72b390bc38afffa5755680388e51d","tid":764561,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":